c: 3
v: 185
t: "Kulli nafsi Raba tammoyse- le, cagalah Qhiyaamah Ayró sin taamoomih galto Siinih dudsumele, tu-Siinik kak daggoyse kalah, tokkel Yalli girak yeyxeereeh jannat culse num, Toysa usuk Nummah yoffoofeh, Addunyâ mano is tu-hinna duquurusiyyi duyyê Baxay edde hataktaanay bayta Akke waytek"